Package cams.users

Class User

java.lang.Object
cams.users.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Staff, Student
public abstract class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Abstract class representing a user in the system. Subclasses must implement specific functionality for different user types.

This class provides common properties and methods for all user types, including basic information such as name, user ID, password, and faculty. It also defines abstract methods for retrieving user-specific data and actions.

The class is Serializable and implements Savable to enable saving and loading user objects to and from files using the SavableObject utility.

See Also:
Savable, SavableObject, Serializable, Serialized Form
